    <h1>Entity</h1>
    <p class="description">A distinct, identifiable thing Google catalogs in its Knowledge Graph — person, place, business, or concept. Entity recognition drives <strong>knowledge panels, AI Overviews, and topical authority</strong> signals across modern search.</p>
